Idea 1:
Take 2 / 24 frames from webcam.
Check every 5th pixel for range of colours (both red and green)
If colour found, check surrounding area.
Get size of each "barrel" and decide closest.
Steer bot towards closest and manueveur into correct zone (g->b,r->y)

